data.description: Fantastic newer home! 4 Bedrooms, 4 Baths, 2 Car Garage. Space for everyone - the main level features a fantastic kitchen space with a center island and plenty of storage, formal dining room, living room and a powder room. The upper level hosts 2 bedrooms, a full bathroom and the primary en-suite with a huge walk-in closet. The completely finished lower level offers a spacious family room, large bedroom, full bathroom and an office/gym space. Fully fenced yard, hot tub and front porch are ready for you to move right in and enjoy. Great location with easy access to highways, downtown and only blocks to Midtown Global Market.
